members.name: Yuri Gagarin
members.details: The first human to journey into outer space, when his Vostok spacecraft completed an orbit of the Earth.

members.name: Alexey Leonov
members.details: First human to conduct extravehicular activity (EVA), exiting the capsule during the Voskhod 2 mission for a 12-minute spacewalk

members.name: Boris Yegorov
members.details: Was a Soviet physician-cosmonaut who became the first physician to make a space flight.
